	<Title>
		Kidney donation: Are there long-term risks?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Kidney donation can save a life, but it&apos;s important to understand the risks.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		I&apos;m considering kidney donation. Are there long-term risks?
	</Question>
